DocDel, Chet, silent readers, seems we are all on line at the moment. DocDel, no I don't think you are out of line at all.  But, I really do want to know details of what happened to the cemeteries.  Why there was absolutely no media on it over here, be it t.v. or even CNN, seems quite odd. What can you tell me?  I certainly don't think you were halucinating or delusional, (and if you were, don't tell me), but if there is some mainland skin head group on &quot;vacation&quot; over there, I would like to work out some of my more agressive feelings, in an intellectual manner of course.<br><br>
No my friend, you have not lost me. I am still ready to play, and kick your butt if it needs it.  I am just glad that you still are here on the playground of life, and not bouncing off the walls alone.  I am glad to not have lose any of you guys, and ladies (oh pardon the sexism) that I have met from this site.  The last 6 months seems more like 6 years, I guess this compression-effect is a spin off from posting in cyberspace.<br><br>
DD, you raise an interesting issue of closeness, comradrie as you put it.  As a combat medic, perhaps you had to avoid that, given the losses you got in the jungle.  Pure speculation on my non combantant thinking, I know, but that is gone now, and we are all here, and the only bullets flying are those of e-mails and posts.  think big, Think the bigger picture, like, how many trollers are we hooking into, how many racists maybe rethinking, or not, or perhaps, if we heat this place up enough, it will get refunded.<br><br>
